Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:05.10,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The Britannian youth, Lelouch, obtained two powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:06.77,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.94,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to give an order to anyone. A power that enforces absolute obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.36,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The other is the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:18.49,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,His personal army formed to destroy the Britannia Empire, ruled by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.79,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch has started to act by using the code name "Zero"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:29.46,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,in order to avenge his mother and turn the world into a place that his sister, Nunnally, can live happily in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:34.18,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of results will those actions bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.30,Default,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, no one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:26.86,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-General, the Japanese Liberation Front was practically wiped out during the operation you led.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.37,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,One by one, the members who managed to escape have been captured by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.67,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Is that sarcasm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:34.47,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Our army is still facing reorganization issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.05,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.48,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,For one thing, didn't the problem originate from the policies adopted after the territory was captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:44.05,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11's subway network, mines, and tunnels. Why were they left untouched?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:47.51,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,In the ghetto, management of the census and the proprietorship of each city is still ambiguous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.69,Default,Guiford,0000,0000,0000,,The breeding grounds for anti-government activities were all left untouched!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.04,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.51,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The subway runs throughout the entire country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.40,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to seal up the areas outside of the settlements, it's estimated to cost...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:01.83,Default,Guilford,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you knew that they were being used by the terrorists as bases and escape routes?! {Literally change into}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.03,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was the instruction of His Highness, Prince Clovis...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:08.68,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... uhm... "The situation will become chaotic if we are too forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.37,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,This might give the Chinese Federation an excuse to strike back at us."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:13.06,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,We've already given them an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:16.12,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is gradually gaining influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:19.20,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,Undersecretary, there are people who are self-governing this area
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:23.17,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,as the representatives of the Elevens under the\Nmanagement of the Ministry of Home Affairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.93,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,A group called the NAC.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:30.36,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to discover signs of the NAC during the last battle. {literally caught the tail}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.91,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,However, the evidence was buried. {Literally under the soil}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.79,Default,Darlton,0000,0000,0000,,It's very suspicious, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.25,Default,Daltron,0000,0000,0000,,If we act on this first...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.25,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.59,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Distinguished families and financial groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.82,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't they be relics of the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.49,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.20,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Those are just baseless rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.66,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,There is no proof that those things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:52.22,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,If we suppress them, the Eleven economy will never advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.79,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It'll affect the tax collection of our motherland too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:04:00.67,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's a widespread principle in the empire for the Numbers to manage their own people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.67,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Then how is the investigation on the Order of the Black Knights going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:08.36,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the shield machine that was left behind, it is clear that Zero was the one behind the incident at Narita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:11.28,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,However, we are unable to find any information other than the corpses of the members that were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:14.69,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that we can neither move against Kyoto, nor chase after Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.31,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.92,Default,Cornelia,0000,0000,0000,,From the results I see, you are all useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:24.21,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect the Britannian Princess to be this capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:28.84,Default,Kyoto01,0000,0000,0000,,The Liberation Front has been broken up. Japan's light has been extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:30.97,Default,Kyoto02,0000,0000,0000,,Excuses again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:34.46,Default,Kyoto02,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's said that they are fleeing, Toudou is still well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:38.34,Default,Kyoto03,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that the Burai Kai was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.88,Default,Kyoto03,0000,0000,0000,,Our hopes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.58,Default,Sakuya,0000,0000,0000,,If it's hope, we still have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.76,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.15,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,You gave them the Guren Mk. II...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:50.06,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the Kururugi Suzaku rescue incident, you have been infatuated with Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.63,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the loss at the Battle of Trafalgar,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:58.73,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabeth III was surrounded at Edinburgh by the revolutionists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.98,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Father, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:05.20,Top,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,With the help of the Britannian colony America, which is now called...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.50,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You look frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.17,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Constipation? For two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.66,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.96,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel lonely because Lelouch isn't around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:31.64,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like... Kallen is absent too... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.48,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,We're pretty careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:37.04,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,The world is still debating over what happened at Narita two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.76,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Suzaku is absent today because of that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.36,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.48,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I think that Lulu and Kallen both being absent is a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.67,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.78,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.24,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.62,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,As I've been saying, why don't you just tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.00,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.54,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.78,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Because... what...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.63,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,"What if I get rejected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:06.64,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It might ruin our friendship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:12.02,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to... laugh that hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:17.54,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice, all of us being here together right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.27,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.77,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,But I hope that you're a little prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.80,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Things that don't change go extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:29.58,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. There's no need to be so serious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:33.69,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! If it bothers you that much, why don't you just ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.25,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how are you faring on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.00,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.67,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lulu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.00,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you absent today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally has a slight fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.72,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sayoko-san had something to do this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.40,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.58,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nana-chan all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.27,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.39,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,President, where are those documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.39,Default,Milly,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there. Please distribute them to all the classes of each grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you're good at ordering people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.81,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I'm blessed to have such a capable subordinate around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:02.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Subordinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.57,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.98,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.41,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Doing that was bad for my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.66,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.08,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.14,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.84,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,E-Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.74,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Was my letter mixed up with those documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:25.16,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:30.97,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:31.88,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.64,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any wild guesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.19,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,That can't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.94,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that person is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.58,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I did it. I really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.07,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do... He'll come, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.04,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't say no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.04,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.28,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going to a concert together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.92,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.72,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.53,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.27,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto has praised us for making good use of the Guren Mk. II.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.00,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.54,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But that white armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.44,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take that to heart. It was a draw. A draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.30,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Shirley suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.52,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Father's job requires him to be away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:44.52,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But he often gives me things like this to make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.63,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,So... how do I say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:47.45,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.33,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.27,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,A love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.64,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is too dense to respond to a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.26,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Tamaki, you're laughing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.11,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,It's an invitation letter from Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.18,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,They want to meet us directly at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a need to make such a fuss over this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.85,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Calling it a fuss... We're talking about Kyoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.81,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll provide us with funds if we're accepted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.79,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Our pathetic financial affairs can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:10.19,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Financial affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.89,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be a problem if you stick to the plan that I've devised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:15.99,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.23,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:19.95,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,We've become a big group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.06,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,The increase in members was above expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:25.31,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Is pretending to be a big shot in front of the newcomers and bringing them to fool around within expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:26.27,Default,Tamki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.37,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I know about it, where you've been going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.54,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll leave the meeting preparations to Ougi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:38.72,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! I'm the one who's been handling the money this whole time. Now you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Produce results if you want me to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.51,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,You actually said that? You're someone who claims to be a comrade, yet you refuse to show your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.77,Default,Tamki,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, what are you going to do? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.41,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.23,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what Zero's real identity is, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.54,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero has the ability to win against Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.67,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,He is {\i1}the{\i0} leader of the Order of the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.81,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a need to know more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.71,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Nina-san, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.26,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.54,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.22,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It's really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.17,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.19,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.60,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,We were originally part of Naoto's unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.68,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if it's his sister, Kallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.48,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Since a second-generation member like you gave the leadership position to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.16,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone agreed to it at Narita...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.63,Default,???03,0000,0000,0000,,But we were practically forced into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:43.33,Default,???04,0000,0000,0000,,He even kept it a secret from us, the executive committee...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.66,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I've found out the twelve possible people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.63,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is how I make my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.50,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's essential to meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.34,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.28,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.12,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:02.26,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I said something out of line back there. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:06.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kallen, do you wish to know my identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.58,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,That person... knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.26,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,No. Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.85,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like your fever has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.41,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:37.09,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Sulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:44.14,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason... Brother, lately it feels as if you have become somewhat distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:51.21,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that my body reacted to that on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.75,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:00.49,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Nunnally, I'll always be beside you, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:03.71,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can I be selfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.32,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold my hand for a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:12.57,Default,Nunnally,0000,0000,0000,,If I go to sleep alone, I feel that I'll have that dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:22.09,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? You're asking me for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:22.84,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.41,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm acting in accordance with the hint you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.26,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the intentions of those people at Kyoto are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.91,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make their power mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:36.31,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,If that is your wish, if it's essential to the goal you're living for, I will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.40,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.93,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,C.C., I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.18,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.38,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.94,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that since I don't know when I'll be back today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.64,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to call and turn her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.75,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,You need to abide by the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:58.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.16,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just perfect. The thing is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.70,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,E-Erm... Hey, Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:08.01,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I... might be late for today's appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:11.13,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But... It should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:13.85,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:25.53,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,It's my master's order that the other members of the executive committee must come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.14,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Just to prevent anything from happening, they are keeping a lookout on the surrounding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.38,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call for them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:36.57,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Bring those heavily mutilated corpses to tent two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.42,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,If there are any items left behind, use it to identify the body immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.31,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Send those who have been identified to tent one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:44.10,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Note the discovery location and time on the certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.54,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,The second medical corps should be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:50.68,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Staff on the ground, please go to your designated positions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:52.72,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really exist... and... turn up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:53.93,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.20,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.80,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't exist in any data!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.28,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Have you done them, the corpse excavation duties?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.48,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Please, if it's possible, I wish to continue the rescue duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.21,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Then please continue until you give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.54,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,That can be considered part of Her Highness Princess Cornelia's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.22,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Lloyd-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.96,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, The Order of the Black Knights... what are they planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.78,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,What do they hope to achieve with these sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.93,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,They are the allies of justice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.63,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,According to what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.22,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,Is this justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:35.80,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Don't tell me you're going to blurt out an embarrassing theory on what justice is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.23,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,We're soldiers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.11,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.15,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed the energy filler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.35,Default,Suzaku,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.13,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Cecile-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.79,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,I've done an investigation on the machines of the Purist Faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.75,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.93,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Radiation Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:05.96,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect her to help the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.60,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,That Rakshata... {Rakshata = proper Indian name.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.80,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy pilot is an ace too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:14.85,Default,Cecile,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Suzaku-kun is mentally unstable, if he were to fight against that opponent again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:18.77,Default,Lloyd,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that it might lose? My Lancelot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.70,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,We've been traveling for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.69,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're still going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.47,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. How disgraceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.24,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.76,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving upwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.36,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for inconveniencing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.38,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,My master is waiting for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.92,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Fuji Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.28,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.50,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,How could we have come to a place like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.35,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,But there can't be any mistake. This mountain, this shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.33,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there is Sakuradite below...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:07.27,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the cursed treasure that led to the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:10.53,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Even though invaders were relentlessly shot on sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.26,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Their strength actually extends to an area like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.12,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto is indeed amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.20,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it repulsive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:24.00,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Mount Fuji, a sacred mountain renown in the past for her scenic beauty and clear water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.20,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it seems to be reflecting the pain our Japan is having,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:31.22,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,after she was conquered by the Empire and continuously suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.92,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.63,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not being able to show my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.93,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,But Zero, the same goes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:46.03,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,I must see and know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.77,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,You shall... show us your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.40,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.71,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero brought us power and victory. That's--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:02.83,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.02,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Ougi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.75,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... Right, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:09.42,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,You shall remove Zero's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.02,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Ougi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.26,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.77,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to believe in you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.21,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,That is why... please make us believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.46,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,A w-woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.45,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,How can that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:29.46,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.75,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,This person is not Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:32.97,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.69,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,She was together with Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.77,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,To the woman there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.61,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,are you the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:38.65,Default,C.C.,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.58,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are not Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.87,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, messenger from Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:47.37,Default,C.C,0000,0000,0000,,Kirihara Taizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.71,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let anyone who knows the identity of the master go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.81,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since she's not Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.67,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.84,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:03.83,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:06.23,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Not only weak, but the way you think and act is outdated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.52,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.48,Default,Kallen,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.24,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:15.00,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.58,Default,???02,0000,0000,0000,,He'll shoot using the remote control!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.61,Default,???01,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, no one is to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.82,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Kirihara Taizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:27.48,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You became famous as the founder of Kirihara Industries through the extraction of Sakuradite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.86,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,You were the shadow supporter of Kururugi's political policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,However, you switched your allegiance after Japan's defeat in the war
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.01,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,and became a proactive supporter of the colonization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Commonly called "Kirihara the Traitor".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.35,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But your true identity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:45.42,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The head figure of the six major families of Kyoto that support the resistance nationwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Pretending to be obedient is something that comes naturally to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.87,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, what do {\i1}you{\i0} know about Master's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.92,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.20,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It is as you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:57.40,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.70,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.49,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he didn't show us his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.42,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fighting if you are not Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.96,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.12,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The destruction of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:14.91,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you are capable of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.73,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:20.44,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because I have a reason that I must do it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.55,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I'm dealing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.47,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:29.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Lord Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:30.75,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.86,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was left behind eight years ago as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.32,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.98,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your care then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.05,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,If the person you were dealing with wasn't me, did you intend to hold him hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:42.95,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.59,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I am only capable of voicing my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:51.81,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Has the seed from eight years ago started to flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.68,Default,Tamaki,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:57.55,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Ougi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:58.79,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:02.53,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,This person is definitely an enemy of Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.55,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,I accept why he couldn't reveal himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.48,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.30,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Follow Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:13.56,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,We will assist by providing information and identifying military strongpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.23,Default,Ougi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.15,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful, Lord Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.39,Default,Kirihara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you embarking on it? The path of carnage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:26.24,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,If that is my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:33.32,Top,???,0000,0000,0000,,The second, fifth, seventh, eighth, and ninth squadrons are to continue identification duties at the management center.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.42,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you spell Fenette? It's indeed this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.13,Default,Villetta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, because the situation is like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.68,Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:43.59,Default,???,0000,0000,0000,,Then please confirm the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.31,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.37,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, things are going to move from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.81,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of the Black Knights is now truly an organization that moves according to my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:19.03,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.46,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.74,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,No, let's put that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.68,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's find a place to shelter from the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.44,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.84,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is an ally of the weak, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.02,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.43,Default,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.72,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:42.32,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did he kill my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.73,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Father... was kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:49.18,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,He never hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.70,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't do anything bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.00,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,But he was buried...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.67,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Unable... to... breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:58.47,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.29,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.54,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:04.25,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.81,0:22:06.22,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.41,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.34,Default,Shirley,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:23:57.90,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:58.79,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:01.41,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:02.29,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:05.30,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to disappear from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:07.04,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is abandon the existence called "Zero".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:12.08,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,Once I silence Kirihara, I can go back to being Lelouch Lamperouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:14.05,Preview,Lelouch,0000,0000,0000,,But... however...
